[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"where do i get the shopifu admin api token ai went to https://dev.shopify.com/dashboard but the secret key was rejected whein input into the genspark api token field to the shopify store configuration Below is the exact click‑by‑click SOP to get the Shopify Admin API Access Token (not the secret key). The secret key from a Partner dashboard will be rejected in the GenSpark Shopify token field — you need the Admin API Access Token from a Custom App inside your Shopify store. ✅ Step‑by‑Step SOP (Click‑by‑Click) Step\tClick Path\tWhat to Do\tExpected Input\tExpected Output 1\tShopify Admin → Settings → Apps and sales channels\tClick “Develop apps” (enable if prompted)\tNone\t“Develop apps” screen opens 2\tDevelop apps → Create an app\tName the app (e.g., “GenSpark Integration”)\tApp name\tApp created 3\tApp → Configuration → Admin API access scopes\tAdd required scopes (at minimum: read_themes, write_themes, read_files, write_files)\tSelect scopes\tScopes saved 4\tApp → API credentials → Install app\tClick Install app\tConfirm install\tApp installed 5\tApp → API credentials\tCopy Admin API access token\tNone\tToken shown (starts with shpat_...) ✅ Why your secret key was rejected Secret key = from Partner / Dev dashboard Admin API access token = from Custom App in Shopify Admin GenSpark needs the Admin API access token, not the Partner secret key ✅ Quick sanity check (token format) Your token should look like: Copy shpat_XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX If it starts with anything else (e.g. shpca, shpua, or just a secret key), it’s the wrong token. Next Step (I can do this for you) Reply with: Your store URL (e.g., mystore.myshopify.com) Confirmation that you copied the Admin API access token I’ll then configure it instantly inside the Shopify setup flow for you. If you want, I can also provide a 1‑page visual infographic + flowchart of the process. AI Developer Let Claw handle it Free Today GPT-5.2 Codex Speak AI Developer Shopify Preview File Explorer GitHub Scripts Skills Shopify Store Configuration Create Voice Agent + Add Store Add Shopify Store 1 Store URL Admin API Token Save API Key How to Get Your Shopify API Tokens 1 Install QuickToken App Search for 'QuickToken' in the Shopify App Store and install it to your store. Install QuickToken 2 Get Your Shopify Info Open QuickToken from your Shopify admin. Your Store URL and Access Token are displayed on the homepage. Copy and paste them into the form above."}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=28faa3c4-bd91-406e-a68f-65309ef19d03","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=28faa3c4-bd91-406e-a68f-65309ef19d03"}]}]}]
